  "body": "### Component\n\nCast\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nI often forget the exact incantation required to pass a wei value from `cast balance` back into `cast` to get out the human readable ether value. It'd be nice if there was an `--ether` or `--unit` flag for commands like `cast balance` to make it a little easier to reach for.\r\n\r\nMostly a quality of life thing, so not super urgent!\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
